DAILY BUG REPORT — ${now.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { timeZone: 'America/Chicago' })}

=== SUMMARY ===
Total Bugs: ${bugs.length}
New Today: ${newToday}
From Backlog: ${backlog}

=== BY STATUS ===
${statusBreakdown}

=== BY ASSIGNEE ===
${assigneeBreakdown}

=== BY FOLDER/PROJECT ===
${folderBreakdown}

